729
00:54:21,920 --> 00:54:24,560
Kita pasti dipukuli sampai mati.

730
00:54:24,560 --> 00:54:26,020
Kita berdua keluar dalam keadaan hidup.

731
00:54:26,659 --> 00:54:28,960
